    "body": "> Do we have access to browserstack or similar tool to test it live on other browsers?\r\n\r\nWe do have a browserstack account, other than that I recommend VirtualBox + https://developer.microsoft.com/en-us/microsoft-edge/tools/vms/.\r\n\r\nInstall this locally from an optic fiber source and then you can start IE9/10/11/Edge in 10s (literally) and even access a local server on your host machine.",
